{
  "texts": [
    "These documented challenges then informed the suggested solutions to these prominent pain points.",
    "To categorize challenges pertaining to pain points, analogous studies on Agile projects were analyzed based on literature research, with their results displayed in Fig. 1.",
    "This fishbone has been constructed based on the pain points shown in Table 2 (see further).",
    "The classification system somewhat mirrors the one by Sithambaram et al., which includes categories like project, people, process, organizational, and technical [16].",
    "However, this study replaces \"organizational\" and \"technical\" with \"endurance\" and \"effort estimation\"."
  ]
}